  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In most normal golf games, you aim your swing, and the wind is decided for you. Breezy flips this concept on its head to create an inventive precision platformer like nothing you've played before. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/e0f02919cf25e810a04d52eb181c0390.poster.avif?t=1762494413\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/e0f02919cf25e810a04d52eb181c0390.webm?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/e0f02919cf25e810a04d52eb181c0390.mp4?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controlling the wind means you can also control boats and even UFOs with the ease of tilting an analog stick. Breezy takes advantage of this in its 180 unique holes. The 4 unlockable bonus characters change up the gameplay even further, especially when you combine them with the wacky random modifiers in the Remix Rush side mode. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/9f400d50db6cadce2357230a32ab0437.poster.avif?t=1762494413\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/9f400d50db6cadce2357230a32ab0437.webm?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/9f400d50db6cadce2357230a32ab0437.mp4?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breezy holds a wealth of Golden Tees in hidden or hard-to-reach places. They're a test of skill, creativity, and strategy, and each one rewards you with a new character, course, or song. Oh, did I mention that Breezy has a jammin' retro-style soundtrack? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/ce93c60205ad3d5f2a6052b45bbf22e3.poster.avif?t=1762494413\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/ce93c60205ad3d5f2a6052b45bbf22e3.webm?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/ce93c60205ad3d5f2a6052b45bbf22e3.mp4?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the great platformers of the past decades, Breezy has surprises around every corner while still emphasizing and riffing on its core gameplay every step of the way. Breezy is not a long game, but it's jam-packed with interesting challenges, memorable moments, and replayability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/87d1afdad64bb9ab75490b59eec24146.poster.avif?t=1762494413\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/87d1afdad64bb9ab75490b59eec24146.webm?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/87d1afdad64bb9ab75490b59eec24146.mp4?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In most normal golf games, you aim your swing, and the wind is decided for you. Breezy flips this concept on its head to create an inventive precision platformer like nothing you've played before. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/e0f02919cf25e810a04d52eb181c0390.poster.avif?t=1762494413\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/e0f02919cf25e810a04d52eb181c0390.webm?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/e0f02919cf25e810a04d52eb181c0390.mp4?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controlling the wind means you can also control boats and even UFOs with the ease of tilting an analog stick. Breezy takes advantage of this in its 180 unique holes. The 4 unlockable bonus characters change up the gameplay even further, especially when you combine them with the wacky random modifiers in the Remix Rush side mode. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/9f400d50db6cadce2357230a32ab0437.poster.avif?t=1762494413\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/9f400d50db6cadce2357230a32ab0437.webm?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/9f400d50db6cadce2357230a32ab0437.mp4?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breezy holds a wealth of Golden Tees in hidden or hard-to-reach places. They're a test of skill, creativity, and strategy, and each one rewards you with a new character, course, or song. Oh, did I mention that Breezy has a jammin' retro-style soundtrack? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/ce93c60205ad3d5f2a6052b45bbf22e3.poster.avif?t=1762494413\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/ce93c60205ad3d5f2a6052b45bbf22e3.webm?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/ce93c60205ad3d5f2a6052b45bbf22e3.mp4?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the great platformers of the past decades, Breezy has surprises around every corner while still emphasizing and riffing on its core gameplay every step of the way. Breezy is not a long game, but it's jam-packed with interesting challenges, memorable moments, and replayability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/87d1afdad64bb9ab75490b59eec24146.poster.avif?t=1762494413\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/87d1afdad64bb9ab75490b59eec24146.webm?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408080/extras/87d1afdad64bb9ab75490b59eec24146.mp4?t=1762494413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
